Nite,

Mostapha could answer your questions about visualizing Multi-objective results better than I could.  He's got a new visualizer coming out called Design Explorer:

[https://github.com/mostaphaRoudsari/Honeybee/issues/292](https://github.com/mostaphaRoudsari/Honeybee/issues/292)



Abraham,

I could not replicate your error because I need to know the weather file that you are using.  The newly-included parsing of ground temperature data is failing because it is not a conventional EPW format.  Please let me know the weather file and I will fix it.



-Chris
